content: Drop down into the mouth of the stone tiger, which leads to a very narrow tunnel passage inside the bowels of the temple. There are few Withered Corpses here to jump out at you from behind pots, but won’t be too much of a problem.

Drop down into the mouth of the stone tiger, which leads to a very narrow tunnel passage inside the bowels of the temple. There are few Withered Corpses here to jump out at you from behind pots, but won’t be too much of a problem.
